Map {
User Stories {
Display Unsupported Orders: As a user, I want to be able to view all orders that are not supported by the Rugby application.
Select Travel Time: As a user, I want to be able to select a travel time for my rugby game.
View Team Stats: As a user, I want to be able to view team stats such as wins, losses, and points scored.
Create Team Profile: As a user, I want to be able to create a team profile with information such as team name, players, and contact information.
View Match Schedules: As a user, I want to be able to view upcoming match schedules.
View Player Stats: As a user, I want to be able to view individual player stats such as goals, assists, and points scored.
Create Player Profile: As a user, I want to be able to create a player profile with information such as name, age, and position.
View Team Rankings: As a user, I want to be able to view team rankings in the league.
}

Admin Stories {
Manage Team Profiles: As an admin, I want to be able to manage team profiles, including adding and removing players.
Manage Match Schedules: As an admin, I want to be able to manage match schedules, including adding and removing matches.
Manage Player Profiles: As an admin, I want to be able to manage player profiles, including adding and removing players.
Manage Team Rankings: As an admin, I want to be able to manage team rankings, including adding and removing teams.
}
}
